OL,3,CSchoolchildren find gun and ammunition
OL,4,Cin woods
OL,6,FPolice have praised the actions of two
OL,7,F11-year-old boys who found a gun and
OL,8,Fammunition while playing in a woodland
OL,9,Fpark.
OL,11,FThe revolver and ammunition were found
OL,12,Fby the children in Halewood Park
OL,13,FTriangle woods in Knowsley, a
OL,14,Fspokeswoman said.
OL,16,FThe boys ran home and their families
OL,17,Falerted police.
