OL,6,FIn a search of the area, officers then
OL,7,Ffound a second firearm - a self-
OL,8,Floading pistol with a magazine and
OL,9,Fammunition, the force added.
OL,11,FMark Baker, Head of Investigations for
OL,12,FMerseyside Police, said: "The
OL,13,Frecoveries of these guns in a wooded
OL,14,Farea that is regularly used by members
OL,15,Fof the public, including children, is
OL,16,Fbeyond belief.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
