OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F391A1710491837
OL,3,CSchoolchildren find gun and ammunition
OL,4,Cin woods
OL,6,F"But to be honest it demonstrates the
OL,7,Fcomplete disregard that those involved
OL,8,Fin serious organised crime have for
OL,9,Fthe majority of our communities, who
OL,10,Fare decent, hardworking people.
OL,12,F"Thanks to the prompt actions of these
OL,13,Ftwo young boys who had the common
OL,14,Fsense to not play with the weapon and
OL,15,Fto go home and alert an adult, we were
OL,16,Fable to take the revolver off our
OL,17,Fstreets.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
