OL,3,CSchoolchildren find gun and ammunition
OL,4,Cin woods
OL,6,F"A further search of the area resulted
OL,7,Fin the recovery of a second gun, a
OL,8,Fself-loading pistol, magazine and
OL,9,Fammunition.
OL,11,F"We know that offenders involved in
OL,12,Fserious and organised crime sometimes
OL,13,Fuse public spaces to hide firearms so
OL,14,Fthat they can distance the gun from
OL,15,Fthemselves and avoid being caught by
OL,16,Fpolice.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
