PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F391A1710491837
OL,3,CSchoolchildren find gun and ammunition
OL,4,Cin woods
OL,6,F"Following the five fatal shootings in
OL,7,FMerseyside in 2022 you would have
OL,8,Fthought that these people would have
OL,9,Fgot the message - they are not wanted
OL,10,Fin our communities and we will not
OL,11,Fstop until we find those who are
OL,12,Fprepared to be involved in gun crime
OL,13,Fon our streets.
OL,15,F"Leaving viable weapons in open public
OL,16,Fspaces is despicable and could put
OL,17,Finnocent members of the public at
OL,18,Frisk, and that is one of the reasons
OL,19,Fwhy we are relentless in our pursuit
OL,20,Fof these toxic individuals."
